==Awards and honors== Sanz received "high" honors at ''[[High Times]]'' magazine's 2003 [[Stony Awards]], collecting the "Stoner of the Year" award.<ref>{{cite web |url=http://hightimes.com/entertainment/aactress/160 |title=Archived copy |accessdate=2010-01-04 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20101216073312/http://hightimes.com/entertainment/aactress/160 |archivedate=2010-12-16 |df= }}</ref>
==In popular culture== *Sanz was parodied on the show ''[[Celebrity Deathmatch]]'', in which he was shown as losing a fight to [[Chris Farley]].
